chool. You didn't go to admin school."}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-ledger fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"01"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"You're charting after hours."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"The average PCP spends nearly 2 hours on the EHR for every hour of patient care. Your evenings aren't yours anymore."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"2 hrs/day lost"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"02"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"Prior auths are eating your day."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"Each prior auth takes 16-23 minutes of staff time. You do 30+ a week. That's a full-time person buried in hold music."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"~10 hrs/week"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"03"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"Claim denials keep climbing."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"The national denial rate is creeping toward 17%. Most of yours are recoverable — if someone actually worked them."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"~17% denied"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"04"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"Your MA is doing too much."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"She's rooming patients, calling pharmacies, triaging messages, scrubbing claims, and verifying insurance. She's about to quit. You know it."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"burnout risk"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"05"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"Coding errors are quietly costing you."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"Wrong modifier. Wrong place-of-service. Wrong level. Each error is $40-$200 in lost revenue — multiplied by every un-audited claim."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"$$40-200/claim"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"06"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"Hiring is broken."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"You posted for a biller in March. Filled it in June. Trained until November. They left in February. You're hiring again."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"14-mo tenure"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pain-row","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"pn","children":"07"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"ptitle","children":"You're not \"burned out.\" You're always behind."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pdesc","children":"You don't need yoga. You don't need a wellness app. You need 20 hours of administrative time off your plate every week."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pstat","children":"20 hrs/week"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"block warm","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"What's actually happening behind the scenes"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display","children":["You don't need a better EHR. ",["$","em",null,{"children":"You need an operational layer."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bts-data fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"lhs","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"You think you have a scheduling problem. You think you need to see fewer patients. You think you need a better EHR."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["You don't. ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"You have an operational layer that hasn't kept up with the practice you've built."}]," Every system is running